title: Madras High Court Recruitment 2025 - Apply Online for 41 Assistant Programmer Posts
description: The Madras High Court has declared the latest job notification for 2025. To fill up the vacancies for 41 Assistant Programmer Jobs. Those candidates who have qualified in the B.Sc, M.Sc, MCA, B.E/ B.Tech, M.E/ M.Tech can grab this chance and apply for the Madras High Court Recruitment 2025 . Here we include the age limit, selection process, salary structure, education details, application fee, and how to apply for these posts.
